Package fi.grimripper.loww.templates

Contains tile templates.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MovementTemplate
    A template for mobile objects.
    ObstacleTemplate
    A basic tile template for various obstacles.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FourSquareTemplate
    A template of four squares.
    HexAndNeighborsTemplate
    A template that includes a hex and all its neighbors, except remote neighbors.
    HorizontalTwoTileTemplate
    A template that consists of two horizontally adjacent tiles.
    SingleTileTemplate
    A template that consists of a single tile.
    SquareAndNeighborsTemplate
    A template that includes a square and all its neighbors, except remote neighbors.
    Templates
    Utility class for templates, which also contains instances of basic template implementations.
